      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "jjeUIIRGaq7S"
      },
      "execution_count": 2,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "# Poisson likelihood\n",
        "\n",
        "$L(λ|\\textbf{X}=\\textbf{x})=\\frac{e^{-10λ}λ^{\\sum_{i=1}^{10} x_i}}{\\prod_{i=1}^{10}!x_i}∝e^{-10λ}λ^{\\sum_{i=1}^{10} x_i}$\n",
        "\n",
        "Dado que el denominador de la expresión no depende de λ, la función de verosimlitud es proporcional al numerador."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "RmpfxLPeYs6O"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 35,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "QxVXJ5lAYo7w"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "def generate_likelihood(lower_bound:float=1e-5, upper_bound:int=5, resolution:int=100, n:int=10, sum_x:int = 10, log_likelihood:bool = False):\n",
        "\n",
        "  \"\"\"\n",
        "    Calculate the (log) likelihood for a Poisson model.\n",
        "\n",
        "    Parameters:\n",
        "    lower_bound (float): Lower bound for the range of Theta values. Default: 1e-5.\n",
        "    upper_bound (int): Upper bound for the range of Theta values. Default: 5.\n",
        "    resolution (int): Number of points to consider within the range. Default: 100.\n",
        "    n (int): Number of observations. Default: 10.\n",
        "    sum_x (int): Sum of observed values. Default: 10.\n",
        "    log_likelihood (bool): Flag to determine if the logarithm of the likelihood should be calculated. Default: False.\n",
        "\n",
        "    Returns:\n",
        "    Tuple: A tuple containing two arrays - Theta and likelihood.\n",
        "      Theta (ndarray): Array of Theta values.\n",
        "      likelihood (ndarray): Array of (log) likelihood values.\n",
        "\n",
        "    This function calculates the (log) likelihood for a Poisson model given a value of the sufficient statistic.\n",
        "  \"\"\"\n",
        "\n",
        "  Theta = np.linspace(lower_bound, upper_bound, resolution)\n",
        "  likelihood = np.exp(-n*Theta)*Theta**(sum_x)\n",
        "\n",
        "  if log_likelihood:\n",
        "    likelihood = np.log(likelihood)\n",
        "\n",
        "  return Theta, likelihood"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Sum x = 10\n",
        "\n",
        "Theta, likelihood_10 = generate_likelihood(log_likelihood=False)\n",
        "Theta, log_likelihood_10 = generate_likelihood(log_likelihood=True)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Sum x = 15\n",
        "\n",
        "Theta, likelihood_15 = generate_likelihood(log_likelihood=False, sum_x=15)\n",
        "Theta, log_likelihood_15 = generate_likelihood(log_likelihood=True, sum_x=15)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Sum x = 20\n",
        "\n",
        "Theta, likelihood_20 = generate_likelihood(log_likelihood=False, sum_x=20)\n",
        "Theta, log_likelihood_20 = generate_likelihood(log_likelihood=True, sum_x=20)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "gUnf-gT2kmzU"
      },
      "execution_count": 24,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "figure, axis = plt.subplots(3, 2, figsize=(20,10))\n",
        "\n",
        "axis[0,0].plot(Theta, likelihood_10)\n",
        "axis[0,0].set_title(\"Likelihood\")\n",
        "axis[0,0].grid(lw=0.3)\n",
        "axis[0,0].set_xlabel('λ')\n",
        "axis[0,1].plot(Theta, log_likelihood_10)\n",
        "axis[0,1].set_title(\"Log-likelihood\")\n",
        "axis[0,1].grid(lw=0.3)\n",
        "axis[0,1].set_xlabel('λ')\n",
        "\n",
        "axis[1,0].plot(Theta, likelihood_15)\n",
        "axis[1,0].grid(lw=0.3)\n",
        "axis[1,0].set_xlabel('λ')\n",
        "axis[1,1].plot(Theta, log_likelihood_15)\n",
        "axis[1,1].grid(lw=0.3)\n",
        "axis[1,1].set_xlabel('λ')\n",
        "\n",
        "axis[2,0].plot(Theta, likelihood_20)\n",
        "axis[2,0].grid(lw=0.3)\n",
        "axis[2,0].set_xlabel('λ')\n",
        "axis[2,1].plot(Theta, log_likelihood_20)\n",
        "axis[2,1].grid(lw=0.3)\n",
        "axis[2,1].set_xlabel('λ')\n",
        "\n",
        "plt.show()"
      ],
